                  <strong>Minimum interim communication:</strong> Monthly email updates on legislative developments, relevant committee hearings, regulatory changes, and political dynamics. Quarterly strategy calls. Annual in-person meetings to review the year and plan ahead. You're not charging full retainer during interim, but you're staying top-of-mind and demonstrating ongoing value.
                </p>
